{"tid":1753641,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"衷心感謝有出嚟投票嘅香港人","createTime":"2019-11-25T03:49:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T04:03:00.000Z","uid":27026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3533bf26fe15df4f069004c6c177701768e5c2f7","tid":1753641,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投比獻世派班垃圾可以出返去先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以睇下以下兩張圖就知有幾多香港人今次走咗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上屆區議會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnHB5bL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnHB5bL.png&h=1043bb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今屆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVassqb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVassqb.png&h=7a55d49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由咁大量紅去到幾乎全黃，真心要多謝每一位有出過嚟投票嘅選民。我仲知有唔少人專登搭飛機返嚟投票，第一次見到香港人嘅凝聚力。大家由政治冷感，到今時今日出嚟表態，見到張圖都覺得好感動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過場仗仲未完，我地仲有出年嘅立法會，仲需要不同活動keep住團火，所以懇請大家每人都繼續出一分力，真係有機會改變香港呢個政治形態。<br />\n<br />\n至於未登記或者今年冇投票嘅人，明白大家可能真係投唔到票，但係希望下年可以見到你地。睇下今年嘅選情，差10幾票嘅又有，一兩票嘅又有，所以多你一個真係好多架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果當初我地一早覺醒咗，就未必會有送中條例，損失咁多手足。不過冇如果，既然依家發生咗，我地就要拯救返自己嘅屋企！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"ea7801d49dcf8f36bffe11237cfabfbacec47e2c","tid":1753641,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:50:09.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">咪撚做休息撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n投完票，贏左喇，但我地有新野做。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/free.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">文宣方向：</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 有得一人一票，社會氣氛好左幾多？而且大家都相信投票，年青人到長者教出黎投，所以應該一人一票選特首。<br />\n<br />\n2.我地要將種票、票多過投票人、送禮各種唔公平現象比英美兩國知。<br />\n<br />\n3. Poly手足被困多日，要求警察撤退。<br />\n</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">五大訴求 缺一不可<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBe water be humble </span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1aa6f1a61ae60c6974fda3ae67e24c446efa6d11","tid":1753641,"uid":314830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3533bf26fe15df4f069004c6c177701768e5c2f7","tid":1753641,"uid":27026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T03:49:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">投比獻世派班垃圾可以出返去先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n可以睇下以下兩張圖就知有幾多香港人今次走咗出嚟<br />\n<br />\n上屆區議會<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MnHB5bL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMnHB5bL.png&h=1043bb5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今屆<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nVassqb.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnVassqb.png&h=7a55d49d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由咁大量紅去到幾乎全黃，真心要多謝每一位有出過嚟投票嘅選民。我仲知有唔少人專登搭飛機返嚟投票，第一次見到香港人嘅凝聚力。大家由政治冷感，到今時今日出嚟表態，見到張圖都覺得好感動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過場仗仲未完，我地仲有出年嘅立法會，仲需要不同活動keep住團火，所以懇請大家每人都繼續出一分力，真係有機會改變香港呢個政治形態。<br />\n<br />\n至於未登記或者今年冇投票嘅人，明白大家可能真係投唔到票，但係希望下年可以見到你地。睇下今年嘅選情，差10幾票嘅又有，一兩票嘅又有，所以多你一個真係好多架！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果當初我地一早覺醒咗，就未必會有送中條例，損失咁多手足。不過冇如果，既然依家發生咗，我地就要拯救返自己嘅屋企！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/dog2_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港<br />\n時代革命</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T04:03:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}